        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for presentation copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [5th ed.].</p> 
            <p>Clarifies his point on north and south glacial periods. Supports CD’s view that temperate plants will move up mountains during the alternation.</p>
